          <p>MR. SPEAKER : The honourable Government House Leader.</p>
        </speech>
      </debateSection>
      <debateSection>
        <num title="1389">RESOLUTION NO. 1389</num>
        <speech by="#7577a3e3-867e-4d2e-a20f-cf0febdf9d97">
          <from>HON. MICHEL SAMSON</from>
          <p>HON. MICHEL SAMSON : Mr. Speaker, with this resolution, I will read it and then ask the Leader of the Official Opposition and the Leader of the New Democratic Party to read a resolution as well. Rather than asking for waiver for each one of them, maybe we can ask for waiver following the resolution by the Leader of the New Democratic Party and then we will have a moment of silence following all three resolutions.</p>
        </speech>
        <speech by="#75109949-5b99-4b9c-b9fd-d85a8ce227ab">
          <from>MR. SPEAKER</from>
          <p>MR. SPEAKER : There has been a request for waiver.</p>
